           move      "cli"                to   w-ide-tip              .
           move      rf-cli-cod-cli       to   w-ide-num              .
           move      rf-cli-loc-cli       to   w-ide-lc1              .
           move      w-wrk-sav-loc        to   w-ide-lc2              .
           perform   exe-cnv-fil-msg-000  thru exe-cnv-fil-msg-999    .
       exe-agg-cli-690.
