      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-agg-cli-200.
       exe-agg-cli-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * [cli]                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "CL"                 to   f-xxx-opf              .
           perform   exe-agg-cli-opf-000  thru exe-agg-cli-opf-999    .
       exe-agg-cli-850.
