      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-agg-vet-680.
       exe-agg-vet-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se non presenti coordinate 'geo'            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tentativo di lettura delle coordinate   *
      *                      * geografiche in base alla descrizione    *
      *                      * del comune pulita con controllo sul     *
      *                      * codice provincia                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione codice provincia     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-cap-cfl-prv      .
           move      40                   to   w-wrk-ctr-004          .
           move      zero                 to   w-wrk-ctr-003          .
           inspect   rf-vet-loc-vet   tallying w-wrk-ctr-003
                                  for trailing spaces                 .
           subtract  w-wrk-ctr-003        from w-wrk-ctr-004          .
           subtract  2                    from w-wrk-ctr-004
                                        giving w-wrk-ctr-005          .
           if        rf-vet-loc-vet
                    (w-wrk-ctr-005 : 01)  not  = spaces
                     go to exe-agg-vet-690.
           add       1                    to   w-wrk-ctr-005          .
           move      rf-vet-loc-vet
                    (w-wrk-ctr-005 : 02)  to   w-det-cap-cfl-prv      .
           if        w-det-cap-cfl-prv    =    spaces
                     go to exe-agg-vet-690.
