      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione localita'            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      rf-vet-loc-vet       to   w-det-cap-cfl-wds      .
           move      spaces               to   w-det-cap-cfl-wds
                                              (w-wrk-ctr-005 : 02)    .
           move      w-det-cap-cfl-wds
                    (07 : 34)             to   w-det-cap-cfl-wds      .
           move      w-det-cap-cfl-wds    to   w-det-cap-cfl-cfl      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione                      *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   det-cap-cfl-000      thru det-cap-cfl-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test su esito della lettura         *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-cap-cfl-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to exe-agg-vet-690.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
