      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-cap-cfl-wcp    =    spaces or
                     w-det-cap-cfl-cap    =    spaces
                     go to exe-agg-vet-690.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Confronto del CAP                   *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-cap-cfl-cap    =    w-det-cap-cfl-wcp
                     go to exe-agg-vet-690.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Aggiornamento CAP                   *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      rf-vet-loc-vet       to   w-wrk-sav-loc          .
           move      w-det-cap-cfl-cap    to   rf-vet-loc-vet
                                              (01 : 05)               .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
